column38:
With this bank account you can get insurance cover for travel and your mobile phone. 

Every month you can earn £4 back in Rewards if you pay 2 or more Direct Debits from your Reward Silver account (2 of those Direct Debits need to be at least £2 each) and an additional £1 every calendar month you login to our mobile banking app. You can also earn at least 1% back on what you spend when you use your NW/RBS Visa debit card at one of our partner retailers.

Plus you can get all the time saving features of our Select everyday bank account, such as 24/7 Online Banking and our easy-to-use Mobile Banking app.

Every month you can earn £4 back in Rewards if you pay 2 or more Direct Debits from your Reward Platinum account (2 of those Direct Debits need to be at least £2 each) and an additional £1 every calendar month you login to our mobile banking app. You can also earn at least 1% back on what you spend when you use your NW/RBS debit card at one of our partner retailers

Plus you can get all the time saving features of our Select everyday bank account, such as 24/7 Online Banking and our easy-to-use Mobile Banking app.

You are also eligible if you have previously held a NatWest Student or Royal Bank of Scotland bank account.
